{"lastModified":1775138821991,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe Lagoon 620 “Adriatic Tiger” combine luxury, performance, and practicality. From its lavish outdoor spaces like the flybridge and aft cockpit, to its advanced technology and stylish interior, the Lagoon 620 offers everything for relaxing in luxury and enjoying life on the water.\n\nWhen it comes to water toys and equipment, the Lagoon 620 \"Adriatic Tiger\" is fully equipped with a wide range of amenities to keep guests entertained and active on the water. The variety of water toys ensures that every moment on board is filled with excitement and enjoyment, making time on the \"Adriatic Tiger\" unforgettable.","blueprint":{"name":"ADRIATIC TIGER","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::88ec43d0-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::890b8ba0-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::890c9d10-fdc3-11ef-8183-8bc7ce753142/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::891130f0-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::88d4eb40-fdc3-11ef-8183-8bc7ce753142/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::88ece010-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::890d6060-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::88edf180-fdc3-11ef-958e-2b5b7ba4f6f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfacf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::890bd9c0-fdc3-11ef-81